---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - AI-Free-Forever">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    {/* Hero Section */}
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-indigo-100/50 py-16 mb-12 rounded-2xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        About Us
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Our mission is to make AI accessible to everyone, forever free.
      </p>
    </div>

    {/* Main Content */}
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      {/* Who We Are */}
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Who We Are</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          aiFreeForever was founded with a simple but powerful idea: AI technology should be accessible to everyone, not just those who can afford expensive subscriptions or navigate complicated platforms.
        </p>
      </section>

      {/* What We Offer */}
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What We Offer</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          We provide a comprehensive suite of AI-powered tools that help with everything from content creation to academic writing, social media management, and career advancement. Our tools are designed to be intuitive, powerful, and accessible to users of all experience levels.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-500">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Social media content generators</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-500">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Academic writing assistants</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-500">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Career and job application tools</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-500">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Blog and article creation tools</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* How We're Different */}
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">How We're Different</h2>
        <div class="grid gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Forever Free</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Unlike other AI platforms that lure you in with a free trial only to demand payment later, our tools are completely free, forever. No subscriptions, no hidden fees, no paywalls.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">No Word Limits</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Many AI tools impose strict word limits that make them impractical for real-world use. Our tools don't have these arbitrary restrictions, allowing you to create content of any length.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Privacy-Focused</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">We respect your privacy and don't store your generated content. What you create with our tools belongs to you alone.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Simple and Intuitive</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Our tools are designed to be easy to use, with clean interfaces and straightforward workflows that help you get results quickly without a steep learning curve.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Our Vision */}
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Our Vision</h2>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-md">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We believe that AI has the potential to democratize access to high-quality content creation, personal development, and professional advancement. By making powerful AI tools freely available to everyone, we hope to empower individuals and small businesses who might otherwise be left behind in the AI revolution.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Return to Homepage Button */}
      <div class="text-center">
        <a 
          href="/" 
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-indigo-500 text-white rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-600 transition shadow-md"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6" />
          </svg>
          Return to Homepage
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>